## 6. Database Operations

This app uses PostgreSQL with Prisma.

Basic operational notes:

- Do not query production DB directly unless absolutely necessary
- Prefer read-only connections when investigating
- Avoid exporting sensitive data unnecessarily

Backups:

- Automatic backups should be enabled
- Document retention length
- Note where they live and how to restore

